scene.message:
Nanjo: To think the townsfolk{nl}
know this much about St.{nl}
Hermelin. How unexpected.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I'd rather refrain from{nl}
visiting a doctor for a{nl}
while, though...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You're not getting fed{nl}
up with this already, are you?{nl}
You quitting? The hospital?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Damn, I'm getting{nl}
antsy. We gotta get to the{nl}
shrine quick...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Ms. Saeko's a senior{nl}
alum of ours, isn't she.{nl}
I've heard about her.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: That woman the nurse{nl}
saw — wasn't that Sonomura's{nl}
mom?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Once we've healed up,{nl}
let's hurry to Alaya Shrine.{nl}
It's quite close now.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Once we've healed up,{nl}
let's hurry to the abandoned{nl}
factory.{waitkey}{clearbox}But can we really get into{nl}
SEBEC from a place{nl}
like that?{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: Oh, that uniform!{nl}
How nostalgic. I'm an alum,{nl}
you know. My classmate's even{nl}
a teacher now.{waitkey}{clearbox}Saeko Takami — know her?{nl}
Still, Saeko a teacher? I can{nl}
hardly believe it! Hehe...{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: An injured woman walked{nl}
by here just a moment ago.{nl}
I wonder if a demon got her...{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Oh, hello. Your{nl}
friends are as full of{nl}
character as ever.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Now then, what'll{nl}
it be?{nl}
{ctl0e:17}{ret}

Doctor: It'll cost 800 yen.{nl}
Is that all right?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Doctor: A shame, but I can't{nl}
treat you with no money...{nl}
Come back with the fee.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Skimp on treatment{nl}
now, and I hope it won't{nl}
come back to bite you.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: I'm a busy man. If{nl}
you've no business here,{nl}
off you go.{waitkey}{ret}
